@startuml "Deposit Flow (L1 -> L2)"
skinparam style strictuml

|User|
start
:Deposit ETH;

|L1 Server|
:Lock ETH in Vault;
:Record Pending Deposit;

|L2 Server|
:Fetch Pending Deposits;
:Execute Treasury Transfer;
:Update L2 State; (Deduct Balance, Increase Nonce);
:Append to Transaction List;

|L2 Server|
:Group Transactions into Batch;
:Generate ZK Proof;

fork
  |L2 Server|
  :Submit Proof and Roots;
  |L1 Server|
  :Verify ZK Proof;
  :Update State Root & DA Root;
fork again
  |L2 Server|
  :Publish DA Blobs;
  |Archive Node|
  :Store DA Blobs;
end fork

stop
@enduml